description:
Gamersnexus was caught upscaling their graphs! https://twitter.com/3kliksphilip/status/1421904638958313478
I investigate what they SHOULD have used instead to upscale them. Short answer: Cupscale, using the Foolhardy Remacri algorithm.

Cupscale - https://github.com/n00mkrad/cupscale/releases
Instructions on how to set it up - https://upscale.wiki/wiki/ESRGAN_Installation_Guide_for_Windows
The Follhardy Remacri algorithm. Put in the 'models-presets' folder for cupscale - https://u.pcloud.link/publink/show?code=kZgSLsXZ0M1fT3kFGfRXg2tNtoUgbSI4kcSy
